2.10	IMC_Group	International Metalworking Companies	IMC International Metalworking Companies B.V. (Iscar Metalworking Cos. or the IMC group of companies) is one of the world's largest holding companies for metalworking products. As part of Berkshire Hathaway, IMC operates Iscar, TaeguTec, Tungaloy, Ingersoll and more in over 50 countries. IMC member companies have secured management control over themselves. Today, IMC has 140 subsidiaries in 65 countries.	
